"{\"uid\": \"journal-topics.com-articles-glenview-police-raise-4100-for-illinois-special-olympics-at-cop-on-a-rooftop\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"Journal & Topics Media Group | Serving Chicago's Great Northwest Suburbs Saturday, December 6, 2025 Members of the Glenview Police Department take part in the Cop on a Rooftop fundraiser on May 17.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 199, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Journal & Topics Media Group\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 28}, {\"ngram\": \"Chicago's Great Northwest Suburbs\", \"from\": 39, \"to\": 72}, {\"ngram\": \"December\", \"from\": 83, \"to\": 91}, {\"ngram\": \"2025 Members\", \"from\": 95, \"to\": 107}, {\"ngram\": \"the Glenview Police Department\", \"from\": 111, \"to\": 141}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 147, \"to\": 151}, {\"ngram\": \"the Cop\", \"from\": 155, \"to\": 162}, {\"ngram\": \"a Rooftop fundraiser\", \"from\": 166, \"to\": 186}, {\"ngram\": \"May\", \"from\": 190, \"to\": 193}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(Photo by George LeClaire) Glenview police took up tactical positions on the roof, in the drive-thru, and in the lobby of the Dunkin Donuts at Lake and Milwaukee avenues on Friday, May 17, raising $4,100 for Illinois Special Olympics.Glenview officers joined officers at nearly two dozen other locations across the Northwest suburbs participating in the Cop on a Rooftop fundraiser.Glenview officers began their watch at Lake and Milwaukee at 5 a.m. May 17, remaining at the scene until about noon.\", \"from\": 200, \"to\": 699, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 217, \"end\": 225, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeClaire_Historic_District\", \"score\": 0.9999999999940883, \"rank\": 5.907692046804918e-12, \"text\": \"LeClaire\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeClaire_Historic_District\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeClaire_Historic_District\"}, {\"begin\": 228, \"end\": 236, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Glenview_station\", \"s